snippet.title: For Honor x Dead By Daylight Crossover | Halloween 2021 Event
snippet.description:
Play Survivors Of The Fog from 21st October to 11th November and unlock a multitude of rewards!

Get ready to muster all the courage you have, you’ll need it if you wish to escape the trapper. Defeat your enemies and conquer your fears to unlock a multitude of rewards with the Free Event Pass. Have a horrific Halloween!


 
For Honor is now available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X | S and PC.
Buy the game: 
http://ubi.li/nks2c 
For more info: 
http://ubi.li/4y839
